	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=1226><span id= >Rakluz</span></a><br><span id=notbold>41 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [2.94]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Crusaders DO harm touch, and its quite nasty.&nbsp;&nbsp;Some con blue to me at 32, so they cant be 33-35.<br><br>Also, their harm touch has a range on it, so be ready to get hurt if you decide to eat it.  If someone says "well they didn harm touch ME," then the crusader probably used up his harm touch on an unfortunate victim and it just hasnt recycled yet.<br><br>My favorite place for them is the temple in 4 corners area.  clear the whole temple, including and especially the top (make sure your group is competant and has a good chanter), and you are bound to get one.  mobs on temple are usually better exp then TR because they are, for the most part, all higher spawns except for TR's placeholders.<br><br>Watchout for the Tae Ew Archon at the top, lvl 34 wiz mob that definately SEES INVIS.<br><br>Ive been hunting almost entirely in cazic (a couple excursions to rathe mtns for hgs) since level 25, and I am now 32.  AARRGHHH why wont they drop the right arm??!!!!</p>&nbsp;<br>Rakluz Roksmasha - ubertroll - 35 Troll SK - &lt;The Storm's Eye&gt;<br>-=Nameless Server=-</td></td></tr>
